   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 句对分类——语义相似度（Pairwise Classification）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**AFQMC（Ant Financial Question Matching Corpus，蚂蚁金融语义相似度数据集）** 是中文自然语言处理（NLP）领域非常经典且广泛使用的一个评测数据集。它由蚂蚁金服（现蚂蚁集团）在 ATEC 开发者大会上开源发布，目前是中文语言理解权威基准 **CLUE（Chinese Language Understanding Evaluation）** 的核心子任务之一。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.1 核心任务与应用场景\n",
    "\n",
    "AFQMC 的核心任务是**文本语义匹配（句子对二分类）**。\n",
    "在真实的客服场景中，不同的用户往往会用千差万别的描述来询问同一个业务问题。该数据集的作用就是训练或评估算法模型：**给定两句话，判断它们表达的用户核心诉求（语义）是否相同。**\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.2 数据格式与示例\n",
    "\n",
    "数据集通常以 JSON 格式存储，每条样本包含三个核心字段：`sentence1`（句子一）、`sentence2`（句子二）以及 `label`（相似度标签）。\n",
    "\n",
    "* **标签分类：**\n",
    "    * **1**：表示两句话含义相同（正样本）。\n",
    "    * **0**：表示两句话含义不同（负样本）。\n",
    "\n",
    "> **典型样本示例：**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> **正样本 (Label: 1)**\n",
    "> `{\"sentence1\": \"花呗如何还款\", \"sentence2\": \"花呗怎么还款\", \"label\": \"1\"}`\n",
    "> *(说明：字面表述不同，但用户的核心诉求完全一致。)*\n",
    ">\n",
    "> **负样本 (Label: 0)**\n",
    "> `{\"sentence1\": \"双十一花呗提额在哪\", \"sentence2\": \"哪里可以提花呗额度\", \"label\": \"0\"}`\n",
    "> *(说明：字面高度重叠，但一个是询问特定活动的提额，另一个是普遍意义的提额，业务意图不同。)*\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.3 数据规模与划分\n",
    "\n",
    "AFQMC 包含约 4.25 万条经过人工精标的高质量句子对。在 CLUE 基准下，官方提供了标准的数据集切分：\n",
    "\n",
    "| 数据集切分 | 样本数量 (条) | 核心作用 |\n",
    "| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n",
    "| **训练集 (Train)** | 34,334 | 模型的日常训练、拟合与参数更新。 |\n",
    "| **验证集 (Dev)** | 4,316 | 训练过程中的超参数调优以及防止过拟合。 |\n",
    "| **测试集 (Test)** | 3,861 | 最终性能评估（官方通常不公开测试集的真实标签）。 |\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1.4 数据特点与工程难点\n",
    "\n",
    "AFQMC 能够在业界保持长期的影响力，主要归功于其极其贴近真实的业务属性：\n",
    "\n",
    "* **垂直领域壁垒**：语料深度绑定金融与支付场景，充斥着"花呗"、"借呗"、"余额宝"等特定产品专有名词。\n",
    "* **口语化与非标准表达**：数据来源于真实的 C 端客服日志，包含大量的错别字、口语化缩写、标点缺失。\n",
    "* **困难负样本（Hard Negatives）**：数据集内部特意挖掘了大量"字面重叠度极高，但语义截然相反"的句子对，传统基于字词匹配的算法（TF-IDF、BM25）在 AFQMC 上的表现通常很差。\n",
    "* **当前工业界价值**：在 LLM 时代，AFQMC 依然被用来微调或评测 **Embedding 向量化模型**（如 BGE、m3e 等），大幅提升 RAG 系统在智能客服中的检索召回准确率。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 1: 导入工具包\n",
    "import json\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "from torch import nn\n",
    "from torch.utils.data import Dataset, DataLoader\n",
    "from torch.optim import AdamW\n",
    "from transformers import (\n",
    "    AutoTokenizer, AutoConfig,\n",
    "    BertPreTrainedModel, BertModel,\n",
    "    get_scheduler\n",
    ")\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, f1_score\n",
    "from tqdm.auto import tqdm\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 2: 数据集 AFQMC\n",
    "class AFQMC(Dataset):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, data_file):\n",
    "        self.data = self.load_data(data_file)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def load_data(self, data_file):\n",
    "        Data = {}\n",
    "        with open(data_file, 'rt', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
    "            for idx, line in enumerate(f):\n",
    "                sample = json.loads(line.strip())\n",
    "                Data[idx] = sample\n",
    "        return Data\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __len__(self):\n",
    "        return len(self.data)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __getitem__(self, idx):\n",
    "        return self.data[idx]\n",
    "\n",
    "train_data = AFQMC('../../data/afqmc_public/train.json')\n",
    "valid_data = AFQMC('../../data/afqmc_public/dev.json')\n",
    "test_data  = AFQMC('../../data/afqmc_public/test.json')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'Train: {len(train_data)}, Valid: {len(valid_data)}, Test: {len(test_data)}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 3: 加载分词器\n",
    "MODEL_CHOICE = \"bert-base-chinese\"\n",
    "tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(MODEL_CHOICE)\n",
    "\n",
    "s1, s2 = \"花呗如何还款\", \"花呗怎么还款\"\n",
    "enc = tokenizer(s1, s2)\n",
    "print('Tokens:', tokenizer.convert_ids_to_tokens(enc.input_ids))\n",
    "# BERT 将句子对编码为 [CLS] sent1 [SEP] sent2 [SEP]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 4: 数据样本预览\n",
    "print('Positive sample:', train_data[0])\n",
    "# 找一个负样本示例\n",
    "for i in range(len(train_data)):\n",
    "    if train_data[i]['label'] == '1':\n",
    "        print('Another positive:', train_data[i])\n",
    "        break\n",
    "print('Negative sample:', train_data[1])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 5: 超参数配置\n",
    "class Args:\n",
    "    model_checkpoint = MODEL_CHOICE\n",
    "    batch_size    = 16\n",
    "    learning_rate = 1e-5\n",
    "    epoch_num     = 3\n",
    "    warmup_ratio  = 0.1\n",
    "\n",
    "    if torch.backends.mps.is_available():\n",
    "        device = torch.device(\"mps\")\n",
    "    elif torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "        device = torch.device(\"cuda\")\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        device = torch.device(\"cpu\")\n",
    "\n",
    "args = Args()\n",
    "print(f'Using {args.device} device')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 6: 构建模型（BertPreTrainedModel 规范化写法）\n",
    "#\n",
    "# 继承 BertPreTrainedModel 的优势：\n",
    "#   - post_init() 保证新增线性层的权重初始化与 BERT 底层权重分布对齐\n",
    "#   - 可直接调用 from_pretrained / save_pretrained，无缝接入 HuggingFace 生态\n",
    "#   - add_pooling_layer=False：不使用 BertPooler（Tanh 激活），直接取 [CLS] hidden state\n",
    "\n",
    "class BertForPairwiseCLS(BertPreTrainedModel):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, config):\n",
    "        super().__init__(config)\n",
    "        self.bert = BertModel(config, add_pooling_layer=False)\n",
    "        self.dropout = nn.Dropout(config.hidden_dropout_prob)\n",
    "        self.classifier = nn.Linear(config.hidden_size, 2)\n",
    "        self.post_init()\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        bert_output = self.bert(**x)\n",
    "        # [CLS] 位置的 hidden state 作为句子对的整体表示\n",
    "        cls_vectors = bert_output.last_hidden_state[:, 0, :]\n",
    "        cls_vectors = self.dropout(cls_vectors)\n",
    "        logits = self.classifier(cls_vectors)\n",
    "        return logits\n",
    "\n",
    "config = AutoConfig.from_pretrained(args.model_checkpoint)\n",
    "model = BertForPairwiseCLS.from_pretrained(args.model_checkpoint, config=config)\n",
    "model = model.to(args.device)\n",
    "print(f'Model parameters: {sum(p.numel() for p in model.parameters()):,}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 7: 构建数据加载器\n",
    "def get_dataLoader(dataset, tokenizer, args, shuffle=False):\n",
    "    def collote_fn(batch_samples):\n",
    "        batch_s1, batch_s2, batch_label = [], [], []\n",
    "        for sample in batch_samples:\n",
    "            batch_s1.append(sample['sentence1'])\n",
    "            batch_s2.append(sample['sentence2'])\n",
    "            batch_label.append(int(sample['label']))\n",
    "        # tokenizer 自动拼接为 [CLS] sent1 [SEP] sent2 [SEP]\n",
    "        X = tokenizer(\n",
    "            batch_s1, batch_s2,\n",
    "            padding=True,\n",
    "            truncation=True,\n",
    "            return_tensors=\"pt\"\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        y = torch.tensor(batch_label)\n",
    "        return X, y\n",
    "\n",
    "    return DataLoader(dataset, batch_size=args.batch_size, shuffle=shuffle, collate_fn=collote_fn)\n",
    "\n",
    "train_dataloader = get_dataLoader(train_data, tokenizer, args, shuffle=True)\n",
    "valid_dataloader = get_dataLoader(valid_data, tokenizer, args)\n",
    "test_dataloader  = get_dataLoader(test_data,  tokenizer, args)\n",
    "print(f'Train batches: {len(train_dataloader)}, Valid: {len(valid_dataloader)}, Test: {len(test_dataloader)}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 8: 批次数据预览\n",
    "batch_X, batch_y = next(iter(train_dataloader))\n",
    "print('Input shapes:', {k: v.shape for k, v in batch_X.items()})\n",
    "print('Label shape:', batch_y.shape)\n",
    "print('Labels:', batch_y)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 9: 优化器与学习率调度器\n",
    "no_decay = ['bias', 'LayerNorm.weight']\n",
    "optimizer_grouped_parameters = [\n",
    "    {'params': [p for n, p in model.named_parameters() if not any(nd in n for nd in no_decay)],\n",
    "     'weight_decay': 0.01},\n",
    "    {'params': [p for n, p in model.named_parameters() if any(nd in n for nd in no_decay)],\n",
    "     'weight_decay': 0.0}\n",
    "]\n",
    "optimizer = AdamW(optimizer_grouped_parameters, lr=args.learning_rate)\n",
    "\n",
    "total_steps  = args.epoch_num * len(train_dataloader)\n",
    "warmup_steps = int(args.warmup_ratio * total_steps)\n",
    "lr_scheduler = get_scheduler(\n",
    "    \"linear\",\n",
    "    optimizer=optimizer,\n",
    "    num_warmup_steps=warmup_steps,\n",
    "    num_training_steps=total_steps\n",
    ")\n",
    "print(f'Total steps: {total_steps}, Warmup steps: {warmup_steps}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 10: 训练函数\n",
    "loss_fn = nn.CrossEntropyLoss()\n",
    "\n",
    "def train_loop(dataloader, model, optimizer, lr_scheduler, epoch, total_loss):\n",
    "    progress_bar = tqdm(range(len(dataloader)))\n",
    "    progress_bar.set_description(f'loss: {0:>7f}')\n",
    "    finish_step_num = (epoch - 1) * len(dataloader)\n",
    "\n",
    "    model.train()\n",
    "    for step, (X, y) in enumerate(dataloader, start=1):\n",
    "        X, y = X.to(args.device), y.to(args.device)\n",
    "        pred = model(X)\n",
    "        loss = loss_fn(pred, y)\n",
    "\n",
    "        optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "        loss.backward()\n",
    "        optimizer.step()\n",
    "        lr_scheduler.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "        total_loss += loss.item()\n",
    "        progress_bar.set_description(f'loss: {total_loss / (finish_step_num + step):>7f}')\n",
    "        progress_bar.update(1)\n",
    "    return total_loss"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 11: 测试函数（Accuracy + F1）\n",
    "def test_loop(dataloader, model, mode='Valid'):\n",
    "    assert mode in ['Valid', 'Test']\n",
    "    all_preds, all_labels = [], []\n",
    "\n",
    "    model.eval()\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        for X, y in dataloader:\n",
    "            X, y = X.to(args.device), y.to(args.device)\n",
    "            pred = model(X)\n",
    "            all_preds.extend(pred.argmax(1).cpu().numpy())\n",
    "            all_labels.extend(y.cpu().numpy())\n",
    "\n",
    "    acc        = accuracy_score(all_labels, all_preds)\n",
    "    macro_f1   = f1_score(all_labels, all_preds, average='macro')\n",
    "    weighted_f1 = f1_score(all_labels, all_preds, average='weighted')\n",
    "    avg_f1     = (macro_f1 + weighted_f1) / 2\n",
    "    print(f\"{mode} Acc: {acc:.4f}  Macro-F1: {macro_f1:.4f}  Weighted-F1: {weighted_f1:.4f}\")\n",
    "    return avg_f1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 12: 训练\n",
    "history = {'train_loss': [], 'valid_f1': []}\n",
    "best_f1 = 0.\n",
    "best_model_path = 'best_pairwise_cls_model.bin'\n",
    "\n",
    "for epoch in range(1, args.epoch_num + 1):\n",
    "    print(f'Epoch {epoch}/{args.epoch_num}')\n",
    "    print('-' * 30)\n",
    "    total_loss = train_loop(train_dataloader, model, optimizer, lr_scheduler, epoch, 0)\n",
    "    history['train_loss'].append(total_loss / len(train_dataloader))\n",
    "\n",
    "    avg_f1 = test_loop(valid_dataloader, model, mode='Valid')\n",
    "    history['valid_f1'].append(avg_f1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    if avg_f1 > best_f1:\n",
    "        best_f1 = avg_f1\n",
    "        torch.save(model.state_dict(), best_model_path)\n",
    "        print(f'New best saved! avg F1: {avg_f1:.4f}')\n",
    "    print()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'Done! Best avg F1: {best_f1:.4f}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 13: 绘制训练曲线\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 4))\n",
    "\n",
    "axes[0].plot(range(1, args.epoch_num + 1), history['train_loss'], 'o-')\n",
    "axes[0].set_xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "axes[0].set_ylabel('Loss')\n",
    "axes[0].set_title('Training Loss')\n",
    "\n",
    "axes[1].plot(range(1, args.epoch_num + 1), history['valid_f1'], 's-', color='orange')\n",
    "axes[1].set_xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "axes[1].set_ylabel('Avg F1')\n",
    "axes[1].set_title('Validation F1')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 14: 加载最优模型\n",
    "model.load_state_dict(torch.load(best_model_path, map_location=args.device))\n",
    "model.eval()\n",
    "print('Best model loaded.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 15: 预测函数\n",
    "def predict_similarity(sentence1, sentence2, model, tokenizer, args):\n",
    "    inputs = tokenizer(\n",
    "        sentence1, sentence2,\n",
    "        truncation=True,\n",
    "        return_tensors=\"pt\"\n",
    "    ).to(args.device)\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        logits = model(inputs)\n",
    "    prob = torch.softmax(logits, dim=-1)\n",
    "    label = logits.argmax(dim=-1).item()\n",
    "    return label, prob[0][label].item()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 16: 验证集示例预测\n",
    "for i in range(5):\n",
    "    sample = valid_data[i]\n",
    "    s1, s2  = sample['sentence1'], sample['sentence2']\n",
    "    gt      = int(sample['label'])\n",
    "    label, prob = predict_similarity(s1, s2, model, tokenizer, args)\n",
    "    print(f\"Sent1: {s1}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"Sent2: {s2}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"Gold: {gt}  Pred: {label}  Confidence: {prob:.4f}\")\n",
    "    print()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 17: 自定义输入预测\n",
    "pairs = [\n",
    "    (\"花呗如何还款\", \"花呗怎么还款\"),        # 正样本：字面不同，语义相同\n",
    "    (\"双十一花呗提额在哪\", \"哪里可以提花呗额度\"),  # 负样本：字面重叠，语义不同\n",
    "]\n",
    "for s1, s2 in pairs:\n",
    "    label, prob = predict_similarity(s1, s2, model, tokenizer, args)\n",
    "    result = '相似' if label == 1 else '不相似'\n",
    "    print(f\"{s1!r} vs {s2!r} → {result} (confidence: {prob:.4f})\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Step 18: 保存模型\n",
    "model.save_pretrained('./pairwise_cls_model')\n",
    "tokenizer.save_pretrained('./pairwise_cls_model')\n",
    "print('Model and tokenizer saved to ./pairwise_cls_model')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 19: 任务总结\n",
    "\n",
    "| 项目 | 内容 |\n",
    "| :--- | :--- |\n",
    "| 数据集 | AFQMC（蚂蚁金融语义相似度，约 4.25 万条人工精标句子对） |\n",
    "| 预训练模型 | bert-base-chinese |\n",
    "| 任务类型 | 句子对二分类（语义相似度判断） |\n",
    "| 评估指标 | Accuracy + Macro-F1 + Weighted-F1，取 F1 均值选模 |\n",
    "| 最优模型 | 按验证集平均 F1 保存权重 |\n",
    "\n",
    "**关键技术点：**\n",
    "\n",
    "- **BERT 句子对编码**：`tokenizer(sent1, sent2)` 自动生成 `[CLS] sent1 [SEP] sent2 [SEP]` 格式，`token_type_ids` 区分两段\n",
    "- **[CLS] 表示**：取 `last_hidden_state[:, 0, :]` 作为整个句子对的聚合特征，送入线性分类头\n",
    "- **BertPreTrainedModel**：`post_init()` 保证新增分类头的权重初始化与 BERT 底层分布对齐，收敛更快\n",
    "- **困难负样本**：AFQMC 的核心挑战，纯字面匹配方法（BM25）在此数据集表现很差，BERT 的深度语义理解能力是关键\n",
    "- **AdamW + 权重衰减**：bias 和 LayerNorm 参数不施加 weight_decay，其余参数施加 0.01"
